Issue Type: <b>Bug</b>

When I use something like:

```
.container {
    background-image: var(--noise);
};

/* a lot of code */

:root {
    --noise: url(data:image/png;base64, ........ ==);
};
```

I can click on var(--noise), and it show me data:img URI code. But if I use import, and I write 
```
.container {
    background-image: var(--noise);
};
```
in imported file... it doesn't show me code, also I can't click on it by ctrl + lclick to open file, where is --noise defined.

